          <updateDate>2016-07-14T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>SMART Guns Act of 2016</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to modify requirements under the Edward Byrne Memorial Justice Assistance Grant (JAG) program. Specifically, a firearm purchased with JAG funds must, to the extent practicable, be a SMART gun.</p> <p>The term &quot;SMART gun&quot; means a firearm that includes a safety feature to prevent an unauthorized person from using such firearm.<br> </p>]]></text>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2016-12-09T18:59:37Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
